# APIArsenal UI Design Rules

## Layout

Use a professional SaaS layout: **Sidebar**, **Topbar**, **Content area**. Spacing must be consistent across pages.

## Typography

Hierarchy must include: **Page title**, **Section title**, **Card title**, **Body text**, **Muted helper text**. Avoid weak typography.

## Colors

Use a minimal palette. Primary surfaces: **white**, **zinc**, **slate**. Accent color should be limited. Avoid colorful dashboards.

## Spacing

Use generous whitespace. Never crowd components.

## Tables

- Column hierarchy
- Row hover
- Right-aligned actions
- Readable padding

Avoid dense tables.

## Forms

- Grouped sections
- Field descriptions
- Validation messages
- Buttons at logical positions

## Empty States

Every empty section must show: **message**, **explanation**, **action button**.

## Loading States

Use skeleton loaders when possible. Avoid raw "Loading…" text.

## Icons

Icons must come from **Lucide**. Use for clarity, not decoration.

## UI Goal

Feel similar to: **Stripe**, **Linear**, **Vercel**, **Supabase**. Avoid generic admin panel design.
